{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"194db7fdb4","title":"命令","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ba2a9658dd","index":0,"year":1933,"month":8,"day":8,"articleId":"194db7fdb4"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1913-1943卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"1968年武汉","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"657b7bc06e","type":"paragraph","text":"十二、白军是军阀的重队，红罩是工农的单队","index":0,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"194db7fdb4"},{"id":"ad906c79dc","type":"paragraph","text":"主任毛泽东（抄自中国革命重事博物馆）","index":1,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"194db7fdb4"},{"id":"c40baa1e0c","type":"paragraph","text":"命今于的溪总司今部","index":2,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"194db7fdb4"},{"id":"43b1070213","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九三三年八月八日）","index":3,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"194db7fdb4"},{"id":"04c768aba7","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）敌之整个布置见蒋介石八月二号命合，卫另录。龙圈有敌第五师四团五十四师两（昨日未与我重作战的），加上昨天与我军作战的四十七师五十四师敢兵药两团，共货有八团。崇置方太之蔡部，兴国江背洞之赵欢涛部，青塘古龙简之环建仲部均在向我重前进，但明日（九号）不能到达龙圈。","index":4,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"194db7fdb4"},{"id":"3b6b2387a0","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）我重决心以全力消灭龙图之敌。（三）攻击龙简布署如左：","index":5,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"194db7fdb4"},{"id":"82a6636dbb","type":"paragraph","text":"三年及七年任左，今夜宿营于兰石，担任攻击龙周之西北端。三军任右，今夜宿营子小别，担任攻击龙商之东北端。四氧任正面，今夜宿营于表湖，担任攻击龙商之南端。十二量位置于四军之后作总覆备队，今夜应宿营于表湖附近。","index":6,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"194db7fdb4"},{"id":"834d993572","type":"paragraph","text":"各军明晨（九号）四时一律总攻，务于上午十二时以前解决战斗。（四）解决战斗后，各军宿营地区分子左三军团及七重在上固、下固、缺家坪一带。三重在小别。四罩在水西、高车、大蕉玩、下车、中塘破一带。龙圩、表湖、张家车、樊铺一带不胜兵。（五）明日上午作战时总部在表湖。作战后至夜间，在龙简母区政府（开场的南端）后晨移石路玩。","index":7,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"194db7fdb4"},{"id":"c18321d410","type":"paragraph","text":"（六）明日下午七时，各重军长、政治委员、重团总指、政治委员均到区政府总部开会。","index":8,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"194db7fdb4"},{"id":"8198ada2b7","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":9,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"194db7fdb4"},{"id":"17b20482f6","type":"paragraph","text":"总司合政治委具","index":10,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"194db7fdb4"},{"id":"b1f8f76b5c","type":"paragraph","text":"（抄自中国革命军事博物馆）","index":11,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"194db7fdb4"},{"id":"815d0c069e","type":"paragraph","text":"反图攻时给红单的动员令","index":12,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"194db7fdb4"},{"id":"85dbb06fe2","type":"paragraph","text":"敌人已经向我们的基本苏区大举进攻了，我们无斋如何要战胜这个敌人。我们要用一切聚定性旗强性持八性去战胜这个敌人。我们这样做就是能够最后的战胜这个敌人。最后的胜利是我们的。英勇奋斗的赶军万岁！","index":13,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"194db7fdb4"},{"id":"5b5403b555","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东（摘自《中国新民主主义革命时期历史》「初稿）","index":14,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"194db7fdb4"}],"page":{"id":"917e76c283","publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"194db7fdb4","start":122,"end":122}}}},"__N_SSG":true}